title: Boba Fett: Bounty Trail
description:
Boba Fett: Bounty Trail	(1999),	720x424,	0:13:28

Slave I hurdles toward the Caviet system on route to Tatooine. Boba Fett, satisfied with his prize, does not realize the Empire once again coniders Solo a valuable asset, after the escape of Luke Skywalker. 

Vader, obsessed with with turning the young Jedi to the dark side of the Force, has deployed an entire Star Destroyer to retrieve the carbonite imprisoned smuggler. 

The small moon of Caviet holds a bounty Fett cannot resist before his rendezvous with Jabba, but this contract may prove to be more trouble than it's worth
